		"description": "The OCN Client collection walks admins and users through the various use cases of the OCN client.\n\nIncluded is the following requests:\n\n- Admin API\n\t- generate registration token\n\n- OCN\n\t- read data from the OCN Registry\n\n- OCPI\n\t- view OCPI versions\n\t- view OCPI version details (module enpdoints)\n\t- POST (register) credentials\n\t- PUT (update) credentials\n\t- and more...",
